-- London Heathrow Airport to Open First Electronic Cigarette Zone
-- B y   L a n a n h   N g u y e n
-- 2013-11-17T11:34:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-17/london-heathrow-airport-to-open-first-electronic-cigarette-zone.html
Gamucci, an electronic cigarette
maker, said it will open the world’s first airport “vaping
zone” at  London ’s Heathrow this month.  The 30 square-meter (322 square-feet) indoor area will open
on Nov. 25 at Heathrow’s Terminal 4 in the international
departure lounge, Gamucci said in an e-mailed statement.  The company is the fastest-growing electronic cigarette
brand in the U.K., it said in the statement, citing research by
Neilsen.  To contact the reporter on this story:
